<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Document</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #f4f7fb;
      --card: #fff;
      --accent: #0b63d8;
      --muted: #6b7280;
      --radius: 12px;
      font-family: Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: #0b1220;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: flex-start;
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 40px;
    }

    .container {
      background: var(--card);
      padding: 32px;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      max-width: 600px;
      width: 100%;
    }

    h1 {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-align: center;
    }

    form {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    button {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #fff;
      border: 0;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.2s ease-in-out;
    }

    button:hover {
      background: #094fab;
    }

    button:active {
      background: #073a82;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 16px;
    }

    a {
      color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: 500;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Student Attendance Portal</h1>

    <form method="get" action="/">
      <button>HOME PAGE</button>
    </form>

    <form action="/face_recognition">
      <button>Attendance</button>
    </form>

    <p>If you face any issues (use of geo-fencing method) : click <a href="">here</a></p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
